{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":441,"text":"Two years ago, I was invited as an artist"},{"time":3470,"text":"to participate in an exhibition commemorating"},{"time":6330,"text":"100 years of Islamic art in Europe."},{"time":8988,"text":"The curator had only one condition:"},{"time":11428,"text":"I had to use the Arabic script for my artwork."},{"time":14918,"text":"Now, as an artist, a woman, an Arab,"},{"time":18029,"text":"or a human being living in the world in 2010,"},{"time":21671,"text":"I only had one thing to say:"},{"time":24636,"text":"I wanted to say no."},{"time":27446,"text":"And in Arabic, to say \"no,\" we say \"no,"},{"time":29662,"text":"and a thousand times no.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":31982,"text":"So I decided to look for a thousand different noes."},{"time":35778,"text":"on everything ever produced"},{"time":37624,"text":"under Islamic or Arab patronage in the past 1,400 years,"},{"time":42305,"text":"from Spain to the borders of China."},{"time":46186,"text":"I collected my findings in a book,"},{"time":48185,"text":"placed them chronologically, stating the name,"},{"time":51629,"text":"the patron, the medium and the date."},{"time":55099,"text":"Now, the book sat on a small shelf next to the installation,"},{"time":58298,"text":"which stood three by seven meters, in Munich, Germany,"},{"time":61905,"text":"in September of 2010."}]},{"cues":[{"time":65419,"text":"Now, in January, 2011, the revolution started,"},{"time":71323,"text":"and life stopped for 18 days,"},{"time":74146,"text":"and on the 12th of February,"},{"time":75605,"text":"we naively celebrated on the streets of Cairo,"},{"time":78593,"text":"believing that the revolution had succeeded."}]},{"cues":[{"time":82626,"text":"Nine months later I found myself spraying messages"},{"time":86282,"text":"in Tahrir Square. The reason for this act"},{"time":90482,"text":"was this image that I saw in my newsfeed."},{"time":94241,"text":"I did not feel that I could live in a city"},{"time":97137,"text":"where people were being killed"},{"time":99144,"text":"and thrown like garbage on the street."},{"time":102112,"text":"So I took one \"no\" off a tombstone from"},{"time":104438,"text":"the Islamic Museum in Cairo, and I added a message to it:"},{"time":108023,"text":"\"no to military rule.\""},{"time":109690,"text":"And I started spraying that on the streets in Cairo."},{"time":112706,"text":"But that led to a series of no, coming out of the book"},{"time":115737,"text":"like ammunition, and adding messages to them,"},{"time":118706,"text":"and I started spraying them on the walls."},{"time":121106,"text":"So I'll be sharing some of these noes with you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":123812,"text":"No to a new Pharaoh, because whoever comes next"},{"time":126410,"text":"should understand that we will never be ruled by another dictator."}]},{"cues":[{"time":130316,"text":"No to violence: Ramy Essam came to Tahrir"},{"time":134462,"text":"on the second day of the revolution,"},{"time":136330,"text":"and he sat there with this guitar, singing."},{"time":139790,"text":"One month after Mubarak stepped down, this was his reward."}]},{"cues":[{"time":144079,"text":"No to blinding heroes. Ahmed Harara lost his right eye"},{"time":149105,"text":"on the 28th of January,"},{"time":150856,"text":"and he lost his left eye on the 19th of November,"},{"time":154202,"text":"by two different snipers."}]},{"cues":[{"time":157688,"text":"No to killing, in this case no to killing men of religion,"},{"time":161013,"text":"because Sheikh Ahmed Adina Refaat was shot"},{"time":164199,"text":"on December 16th, during a demonstration,"},{"time":167561,"text":"leaving behind three orphans and a widow."}]},{"cues":[{"time":171421,"text":"No to burning books. The Institute of Egypt was burned"},{"time":174704,"text":"on December 17th, a huge cultural loss."}]},{"cues":[{"time":178924,"text":"No to stripping the people,"},{"time":181313,"text":"and the blue bra is to remind us of our shame"},{"time":184807,"text":"as a nation when we allow a veiled woman to be stripped"},{"time":188757,"text":"and beaten on the street, and the footprint reads,"},{"time":192758,"text":"\"Long live a peaceful revolution,\""},{"time":194910,"text":"because we will never retaliate with violence."}]},{"cues":[{"time":198430,"text":"No to barrier walls. On February 5th,"},{"time":201845,"text":"concrete roadblocks were set up in Cairo"},{"time":206038,"text":"to protect the Ministry of Defense from protesters."}]},{"cues":[{"time":211719,"text":"Now, speaking of walls, I want to share with you the story"},{"time":214164,"text":"of one wall in Cairo."},{"time":216966,"text":"A group of artists decided to paint a life-size tank"},{"time":221273,"text":"on a wall. It's one to one."},{"time":223115,"text":"In front of this tank there's a man on a bicycle"},{"time":226979,"text":"with a breadbasket on his head. To any passerby,"},{"time":230093,"text":"there's no problem with this visual."},{"time":232947,"text":"After acts of violence, another artist came,"},{"time":236861,"text":"painted blood, protesters being run over by the tank,"},{"time":241334,"text":"demonstrators, and a message that read,"},{"time":244380,"text":"\"Starting tomorrow, I wear the new face,"},{"time":247727,"text":"the face of every martyr. I exist.\""},{"time":251446,"text":"Authority comes, paints the wall white,"},{"time":254347,"text":"leaves the tank and adds a message:"},{"time":256989,"text":"\"Army and people, one hand. Egypt for Egyptians.\""},{"time":262018,"text":"Another artist comes, paints the head of the military"},{"time":265653,"text":"as a monster eating a maiden in a river of blood"},{"time":269015,"text":"in front of the tank."},{"time":271707,"text":"Authority comes, paints the wall white, leaves the tank,"},{"time":275708,"text":"leaves the suit, and throws a bucket of black paint"},{"time":278336,"text":"just to hide the face of the monster."},{"time":279943,"text":"So I come with my stencils, and I spray them on the suit,"},{"time":283836,"text":"on the tank, and on the whole wall,"},{"time":286261,"text":"and this is how it stands today"},{"time":288335,"text":"until further notice. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":290114,"text":"Now, I want to leave you with a final no."},{"time":294380,"text":"I found Neruda scribbled on a piece of paper"},{"time":297995,"text":"in a field hospital in Tahrir, and I decided to take a no of"},{"time":303224,"text":"Mamluk Mausoleum in Cairo."},{"time":305538,"text":"The message reads,"},{"time":307323,"text":"[Arabic]"},{"time":313732,"text":"\"You can crush the flowers, but you can't delay spring.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":317409,"text":"Thank you. (Applause)"},{"time":321264,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":330285,"text":"Thank you. Shukran. (Applause)"}]}]}